posts.post_title: FS: T206s with EPDG and AB 350 backs
posts.post_content:
Two nice examples of T206s with less common backs for sale:
 
1) Clancy, American Beauty 350 Framed, SGC 50 - SOLD!
 
2) Shannon, El Principe de Gales, SGC 60 - nice looking card all around. Certainly one of the more unique poses in the T206 set - you just gotta love the solid black "KC" moniker on the solid black uniform! $150.00 delivered.
 
First person to send an e-mail to [URL="sschris@att.net"]sschris@att.net[/URL] committing to make purchase ("I'll take it") is the new owner. Good luck!
 
Thanks,
Steve C.
